            <div class="escom-long-form-text">
                <p class="escom-long-form-text__p--l">
                    Since 1994, Dan’s focused on <a href="/product-discovery.html">digital product discovery and definition</a>, user research, information architecture, content strategy and interaction design for content-heavy sites, complex web applications, and digital products. He’s worked on teams large and small to perfect collaboration and productivity. In 2006, Dan co-founded EightShapes with <a href="nathan-curtis.html">Nathan Curtis</a> to serve clients in healthcare, education, not-for-profit and high-tech.
                </p>
